WASM Runtime with JIT Compilation
Build a WebAssembly runtime that validates, interprets, and JIT-compiles WASM modules. Implement a stack-based VM, memory sandboxing with guard pages, and cranelift integration for JIT. Support WASI system calls and provide a host function interface. Handle trap recovery and async execution.

Key Features: Custom bytecode interpreter, FFI with C libraries, mmap for memory management, signal handling for trap recovery, no_std compatibility considerations